Revision history for Path-Any

0.001     2025-03-05
          - Initial release.
          - Path::Tiny-compatible API with pluggable adapter system.
          - Adapters: Local, SFTP (Net::SFTP::Foreign), S3 (Paws), MultiPlex, Null.
          - Adapter-scoped path routing via Path::Any::Adapter.
          - mirror() with optional size/digest skipping.
